| C ✓ | **Chat history cap** + `history_truncated` on pull payload; long-session copy on session detail + health | Done: [plan 12](../plan/12-server-chat-history-cap-complete.md), [plan 25](../plan/25-web-ux-spec-checkpoints-complete.md); [API_OVERVIEW — Pull task](API_OVERVIEW.md#pull-task), [CLIENT_EXPERIENCE §12](CLIENT_EXPERIENCE.md#12-long-chat-sessions) |
