| E ✓ | **Session/job UI**: `error_message`, no silent “missing MR”; PR expectation copy | Done: [plan 25](../plan/25-web-ux-spec-checkpoints-complete.md); [PRODUCT I4](PRODUCT.md), [CLIENT_EXPERIENCE §8](CLIENT_EXPERIENCE.md#8-git-commit-push-and-prmr-outcomes), [Architecture §9a–9b](ARCHITECTURE.md#9a-when-the-worker-attempts-commit-and-push) |
| F | **Workers list** banner for mixed `platform` / heterogeneous pool | [CLIENT_EXPERIENCE §10](CLIENT_EXPERIENCE.md#10-worker-pool-heterogeneity-warnings), [ARCHITECTURE §4c](ARCHITECTURE.md#4c-platform-specific-workers-cli-invocation) |
